# рҹҺ“ SA College of Arts & Science вҖ“ Student Portal

A full-featured student portal built with **Streamlit + Python**.

## вңЁ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| рҹ”җ Student Auth | Register, Login, Remember Me, Photo Upload |
| рҹӣЎпёҸ Admin Panel | Separate login, Dashboard, Students, Results, Leaderboard |
| рҹ“қ Entrance Test | 12 Questions, 4 Sections, 5-min Timer, One-attempt lock |
| рҹ“Ҡ Score Chart | Pie chart breakdown after exam |
| рҹҸҶ Leaderboard | Top 10 scorers with medals |
| рҹҸ… Merit Certificate | Auto PDF for scores вүҘ 100/120 |
| рҹ“„ Result PDF | Downloadable result with QR code |
| рҹӨ– College GPT | OpenAI-powered academic chatbot (Tamil + English) |
| рҹ’¬ Feedback | Student feedback form |

## рҹҡҖ Run Locally

### 1. Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/sa-college-portal.git
cd sa-college-portal
```

### 2. Install dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Add your OpenAI API key
Create `.streamlit/secrets.toml`:
```toml
OPENAI_API_KEY = "sk-your-key-here"
```

### 4. Add college images (optional)
Put these images in the `assets/` folder:
- `assets/college.png` вҖ” College building photo
- `assets/hod.png` вҖ” HOD photo

### 5. Run the app
```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

## вҳҒпёҸ Deploy on Streamlit Cloud

1. Push your code to GitHub
2. Go to [share.streamlit.io](https://share.streamlit.io)
3. Connect your GitHub repo
4. Set **Main file**: `app.py`
5. Go to **Settings вҶ’ Secrets** and add:
```
OPENAI_API_KEY = "sk-your-key-here"
```
6. Click **Deploy** вң…

## рҹ”җ Admin Access

- URL: Click "Admin Login" on the student login page
- Username: `admin`
- Password: `admin123`

> вҡ пёҸ Change the admin password in `app.py` before deploying!

## рҹ“Ғ Project Structure

```
sa-college-portal/
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ app.py                  # Main application
в”ңв”Җв”Җ requirements.txt        # Dependencies
в”ңв”Җв”Җ .gitignore
в”ңв”Җв”Җ README.md
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ assets/                 # College images (add manually)
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ college.png
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ hod.png
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ uploads/                # Student profile photos (auto-created)
в””в”Җв”Җ .streamlit/
    в””в”Җв”Җ secrets.toml        # API keys (DO NOT push to GitHub)
```

## рҹӣ пёҸ Tech Stack

- **Frontend/Backend**: Streamlit
- **Database**: SQLite
- **PDF**: ReportLab
- **QR Code**: qrcode
- **Charts**: Matplotlib
- **AI**: OpenAI GPT-4o-mini
- **Auth**: bcrypt hashing + cookies

